  "general_provisions": "This resolution addresses the need for comprehensive fiscal impact analysis of legislation on local education agencies.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This resolution:<hr><ltbullet>acknowledges the importance of understanding fiscal impacts of legislation on local education agencies;<hr><ltbullet>recognizes the partnership between the Legislature, State Board of Education (state board), and local education stakeholders;<hr><ltbullet>supports the development of systematic processes for collecting and analyzing local education agency fiscal impact data;<hr><ltbullet>calls on the state board to collaborate with local education agencies and stakeholders to provide real-time fiscal impact information to the Legislature; and<hr><ltbullet>requests specific recommendations for implementing local education agency fiscal impact analysis systems.",
